      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">天保.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天保定爾，亦孔之固。俾爾單厚，何福不除？俾爾多益，以莫不庶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Heaven protects and establishes thee,
With the greatest security;
Makes thee entirely virtuous.
​That thou mayest enjoy every happiness;
Grants thee much increase,
So that thou hast all in abundance.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
