      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">天保.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吉蠲為饎，是用孝享。禴祠烝嘗，于公先王。君曰卜爾，萬壽無疆！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>With happy auspices and purifications thou bringest the offerings,
And dost filially present them,
In spring, summer, autumn, and winter,
To the dukes and former kings;
And they say, 'We give to thee
myriads of years, duration unlimited.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
