      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">天保.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>神之弔矣，詒爾多福。民之質矣，日用飲食。羣黎百姓，徧為爾德。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The spirits come,
And confer on thee many blessings.
The people are simple and honest,
Daily enjoying their meat and drink.
All the black-haired race, in all their surnames,
Universally practise thy virtue.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-006__006__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
