      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·006.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">天保.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>如月之恆，如日之升。如南山之壽，不騫不崩。如松柏之茂，無不爾或承。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Like the moon advancing to the full,
Like the sun ascending the heavens,
Like the everlasting southern hills,
Never waning, never falling,
Like ​the luxuriance of the fir and the cypress;—
May such be thy succeeding line!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
